### Create Specialisation (Required for Doctor)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/specialisation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "General Practice"
}

### Create Patient
POST http://localhost:8000/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "gender": "Male",
  "date_of_birth": "1990-01-01",
  "phone_number": "555-1234",
  "email_address": "john.doe@example.com",
  "address_line1": "123 Main St",
  "address_line2": "Apt 4B",
  "state": "CA",
  "country": "USA"
}

### Create Doctor
POST http://localhost:8000/api/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Dr",
  "last_name": "Who",
  "specialisation_ids": [1]
}

### Book Appointment
POST http://localhost:8000/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": 1,
  "doctor_id": 1,
  "appointment_datetime": "2025-12-31T14:00:00Z",
  "reason": "Annual Checkup"
}

### Create Bill
POST http://localhost:8000/api/billing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointment_id": 1,
  "amount": 100.00,
  "bill_status_id": 1,
  "payment_method_id": 1
}

### Search Patient by Name
GET http://localhost:8000/api/patients?search=John

### Search Doctor by Name
GET http://localhost:8000/api/doctors?search=Who

### Create Prescription
POST http://localhost:8000/api/prescriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prescribed_appointment_id": 1,
  "medicine_name": "Paracetamol",
  "dosage": "500mg",
  "frequency": "Twice a day",
  "instructions": "Take after meals",
  "created_by": 1
}

### List Prescriptions
GET http://localhost:8000/api/prescriptions

### Search Prescriptions
GET http://localhost:8000/api/prescriptions?search=Para

### Record Vital Signs
POST http://localhost:8000/api/clinical/vitals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": 1,
  "appointment_id": 1,
  "temperature": 36.6,
  "blood_pressure_systolic": 120,
  "blood_pressure_diastolic": 80,
  "heart_rate": 72,
  "created_by": 1
}

### List Vitals for Patient
GET http://localhost:8000/api/clinical/vitals/patient/1

### Diagnostic Test (Is Clinical Router Active?)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/clinical/test

### List All Vitals
GET http://localhost:8000/api/clinical/vitals

### Add Clinical Note
POST http://localhost:8000/api/clinical/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointment_id": 1,
  "notes": "Patient reports mild joint pain in the morning.",
  "created_by": 1
}

### List Notes for Patient
GET http://localhost:8000/api/clinical/notes/patient/1

### List All Clinical Notes
GET http://localhost:8000/api/clinical/notes


